  ('promotion-8b44517b-moex-00044', 'promotion-8b44517b', 'promotion-8b44517b-moex-112-ad750edf', 'sub-promotion-8b44517b-02', NULL, 'essay', '一般俗稱「綁約」的「最低服務年限」，若勞方違反往往有費用賠償或違
