  ('promotion-8b44517b-moex-00045', 'promotion-8b44517b', 'promotion-8b44517b-moex-112-ad750edf', 'sub-promotion-8b44517b-02', NULL, 'essay', '民國（下同）112 年一連串的職場性騷擾事件遭到揭露，衝擊勞資關係
